title: Unfiltered Moments ( Donkey Nominations, Maino and Jim Jones Interview , Rumors, Positive Note)
itunes:title: Unfiltered Moments ( Donkey Nominations, Maino and Jim Jones Interview , Rumors, Positive Note)
description:
Charlamagne is out today so we had our listeners call up to nominate someone of their own for "Donkey of the Day". Also, we had the Lobby Boyz, Maino and Jim Jones stop by where they spoke on squashing beef, healing inner city violence, "Slide" and more. Next after Angela's "Rumor Report" they end the show with some positivity with the "Positive Note".

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
